I'm sorry but mentally ill people don't get a free pass. I'm actually offended on the behalf of mentally ill people that you hold them so low in your mind.", "Please understand that r/IncelTears takes screenshots from various places. Separate websites outside Reddit like incels.me and especially truecels.org **allow** posts advocating rape, violence, and pedophilia. 

**Braincels doesn't allow those type of posts.** However, people often confuse all content on IncelTears as coming from Braincels, simply because it's the largest incel sub on Reddit.", "@stern-universe, I've got to say, your comments are quite misguided. It's not fair to lump all incels together and label them as mentally ill or dangerous. Braincels does have its issues, but it's not the same as the extremist forums you're referring to. Let's not paint with too broad a brush here.

